."],[563,742,"But you proposed to me yesterday."],[742,846,"Does this mean nothing?"],[942,996,"See?"],[1051,1159,"You already lost the ring."],[1209,1317,"This wasn't meant to be."],[1351,1476,"Oh, that cheap ring?"],[1476,1634,"We got it at the dollar store."],[1676,1764,"Victor, we've been together"],[1764,1876,"for three years."],[1926,2052,"I, I gave up everything"],[2052,2122,"for this wedding"],[2131,2285,"and, and you're you're, leaving me"],[2285,2402,"because I'm a human?"],[2452,2606,"You said that love has no race."],[2606,2727,"Victor, please."],[2740,2781,"Ah!"],[2965,3132,"Werewolves versus humans?"],[3165,3278,"Humans are pathetic."],[3386,3549,"No, no, no this can't be happening."],[3557,3720,"You should stick to what you're good at."],[3728,3862,"Bringing food to stronger,"],[3862,4016,"superior folks."],[4066,4254,"Baby, can we take you to the bedroom?"],[4262,4450,"I don't care if she hears me moan."],[5409,5455,"Ah!"],[5601,5672,"Victor!"],[5672,5747,"Get her!"],[5780,5822,"No!"],[6118,6177,"Let"],[6177,6247,"her"],[6247,6306,"go!"],[7090,7207,"You'll pay for that."]],"4":[[0,108,"Baby, are you okay?"],[129,266,"And who the hell are you?"],[283,358,"Who am I?"],[408,492,"You haven't earned the right"],[492,550,"to know that."],[658,742,"Are you hurt?"],[855,938,"Say the word,"],[938,1005,"and I'll deal with these two"],[1005,1117,"assholes for you."],[1130,1213,"A damn hobo?"],[1234,1326,"How did you even get"],[1326,1447,"into this neighborhood?"],[1459,1564,"You really sank this low?"],[1584,1730,"Messing around with garbage?"],[1785,1926,"I made the right call dumping you."],[2018,2089,"Don't."],[2135,2210,"He's not worth it,"],[2210,2356,"don't dirty your hands."],[2369,2481,"Like anyone else"],[2481,2635,"would ever want you after me."],[2694,2794,"Let's go inside."],[2840,3040,"I don't want this trash dragging dirt"],[3040,3107,"into our home."],[3574,3641,"Are you okay?"],[3724,3803,"I'm sorry,"],[3803,4020,"that bastard isn't worth your 